{"tid":2119614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【總領館火警】美要求中國關閉侯斯頓總領館 中方促撤銷決定：否則作出必要反應","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:14:34.000Z","uid":267658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba07ccdca914dc255249bf2748e801385b6768b","tid":2119614,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/P3LIRTHSK2JRU35N7ZCJ6NT3RU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FP3LIRTHSK2JRU35N7ZCJ6NT3RU%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=b8694e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FP3LIRTHSK2JRU35N7ZCJ6NT3RU%2F&h=0f24a9ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200722/P3LIRTHSK2JRU35N7ZCJ6NT3RU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【總領館火警】美要求中國關閉侯斯頓總領館 中方促撤銷決定：否則作出必要反應<br />\n8分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eWHtzeRYOxBGGf71Maf4rZUd6w8=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I4AUBB7OWJ6F6V4RHL42SRC5WI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeWHtzeRYOxBGGf71Maf4rZUd6w8%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI4AUBB7OWJ6F6V4RHL42SRC5WI.jpg&h=5f90161d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（更新：內容）當地時間21日晚上，中國駐美國侯斯頓總領事館發生大火。當地傳媒「Click2Houston」報道，警方的指，可能是機密文件被燒毀，惟有關情況未得到證實。《環球時報》總編胡錫進透露，美國要求中方在72小時內關閉該領事館。《蘋果》致電中國駐侯斯頓總領事館辦公室24小時值班熱線，但是電話未能接通。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人汪文斌今日在例行記者會，證實美國限時要關閉侯斯敦總領館。他批評，這是美方單方面對中方發起的「政治挑釁」，「嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本原理，嚴重違反中美領事條約有關規定，蓄意破壞中方關係，十分蠻橫無理」。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌又強調，中方敦促美方立即恢復有關錯誤決定。否則，「中方必將做出正當和必要反應」。<br />\n<br />\n他又列舉美國對中國的刁難：不斷向中方甩鍋推責，對中國進行污名化攻擊，無端攻擊中國社會制度，無理刁難中國駐美外交領事人員，對中國在美留學人員進行恐嚇、盤查，沒收個人電子設備，甚至是無端拘押。他表示，這次美方單方面限時關閉中國總領館，「是美對華採取的前所未有的升級行動」。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌又批評，美方認為「美中關係不對等，這是美方的慣用藉口，毫無道理」。汪稱，事實上，單就中美駐對方國家使領館數量和外交領事人員數量而言，美方遠遠多於中方。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》總編胡錫進在微博發帖，寫道:「據老胡剛剛得到的消息，美國政府悍然要求中國72小時內關閉駐侯斯頓總領館，這是一個瘋狂的行動。侯斯頓總領館是中國在美國開的第一個總領館，美方不僅要求關閉它，而且只給出中方3天的撤離時間，這完全是喪心病狂的表現。看來華盛頓已經毫無底線，這屆美國政府真是甚麼都能幹得出來。」 ​​​​<br />\n<br />\n當地電視台「KHOU 11」亦報道，領事館人員接獲通知，須在本周五下午4時前全數撤離，惟報道未有透露原因。而有傳媒查詢時，警方則要記者向美國國務院或總統特朗普查詢。中國駐侯斯頓領事館及美國國務院暫未作回應。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，火警晚上8時許報告，地點為德州侯斯頓蒙特羅斯大道3417號，而該位置正是中國總領事館所。警方透露，他們接獲文件被燒的報告。現場所見，有黑煙從建築物範圍內飄出。有住在領事館旁邊的觀眾拍到現場有幾個打開的箱子或容器火焰，看到有人將東西扔入燃燒的垃圾桶內。消防到場後，未有進入建築物範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n據《侯斯頓紀事報》（Houston Chronicle）指，有目擊者看有人在建築物外面燒紙，事件中未有人受傷報告。警察無權進入位於的該設施。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"c2c84c791a5ed0d2d3232749d0bcc4c2a2db6b57","tid":2119614,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ss4lnlO609xG_CSXZ-4d2k-qexA=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUDXUF6IOHLDKJ4B224EBJWBQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSs4lnlO609xG_CSXZ-4d2k-qexA%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUDXUF6IOHLDKJ4B224EBJWBQU.jpg&h=a7918882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國駐美國侯斯頓總領事館發生火警。（圖片來源：<a href=\"http://www.click2houston.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.click2houston.com&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=cb2373ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.click2houston.com</a>）<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rsQn5do0xpTQfUo4iT0VCE_Al84=/561x1032/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GDVXPF67TDGYPLJ2KRTFO65Q24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrsQn5do0xpTQfUo4iT0VCE_Al84%3D%2F561x1032%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGDVXPF67TDGYPLJ2KRTFO65Q24.jpg&h=9edb2f56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09d3bb66660ee25e9c7269f2281dbdbd0b2fb7df","tid":2119614,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"出咩招回應？驅逐美國註香港領事館？"},{"pid":"1cf9a5c8c059318cd68ef66c0e78d567b3fe78f2","tid":2119614,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09d3bb66660ee25e9c7269f2281dbdbd0b2fb7df","tid":2119614,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"出咩招回應？驅逐美國註香港領事館？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgOwj66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgOwj66.jpg&h=9b20dac6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6363df6a8ffe93635be8ea97ba845156e9f85dcc","tid":2119614,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"講左咁多年，今次終於有山雨欲來既感覺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南海戰雲密佈，美日澳三國聯合軍演<br />\n依家仲要求關閉總領事館，等同驅逐大使"},{"pid":"39d07e9fc2c7709a43c785debff097202e8e26ef","tid":2119614,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d3bb66660ee25e9c7269f2281dbdbd0b2fb7df","tid":2119614,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"出咩招回應？驅逐美國註香港領事館？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9qLmReS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9qLmReS.png&h=5bedbe96&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}